\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Present \& Near Telescopic Future}
\begin{itemize}
  \item Commons become the Regulatory system.
  \item Commons become the Quality Inspection system.
  \item Commons can self regulate their Analysis and Ranking system.
  \item Commons can once again have their own localized business audiences.
  \item Science and Technology development becomes Commons social activity.
  \item Business will be brewed locally \& in decentralized way.
  \item Commons would embrace and form Anti-Ignorance Movement.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}





